hypotenuse of a right triangle, then we can as we've done so many times before,

00:00:12.497 --> 00:00:16.855
use the Pythagorean theorem to find the length of that side. Conveniently, since

00:00:16.867 --> 00:00:20.897
we're using graph paper, made up of these little tiny squares, we have right

00:00:20.909 --> 00:00:24.731
angles all over the place. That made drawing these right triangles super simple.

