Seven is the length of this side. We'll do the same thing for this side. This is

00:00:58.145 --> 00:01:03.046
five. In looking at this modified version of the Pythagorean theorem, we can

00:01:03.058 --> 00:01:07.981
just say that the length of AB, this hypotenuse, is the square root of 7 squared

00:01:07.993 --> 00:01:12.753
plus 5 squared. Simplifying that gives us the square root of 74. Once we find

00:01:12.765 --> 00:01:17.613
the lengths of the legs of all of the other right triangles, calculating their

00:01:17.625 --> 00:01:19.726
hypotenuses is also easy.

00:01:19.727 --> 00:01:26.427
And so, at long last, here are our final answers. The length of AB is the square

00:01:26.439 --> 00:01:32.818
root of 74, BC, square root of 180, CD is the square root of 40, and DA is the

00:01:32.830 --> 00:01:34.403
